## Additional Context
- **CORS Bypass:** All LLM requests through Tauri/Rust HTTP, never browser fetch
- **Thinking Mode:** Per-provider support (Anthropic native blocks, GLM/DeepSeek via params)
- **Context Windows:** Dynamically read from DB, provider-specific defaults
- **Window Sync:** useWindowStateSync keeps main/detached windows synchronized
- **Thread Persistence:** Full token/context usage tracking in SQLite threads table
- **Tool Approvals:** Per-tool configurable approval modes (auto/deny/prompt)
